and also act as a nice respite for when you've crashed R 20 times in a row using C++. So

00:13:42.299 --> 00:13:46.299
writing about your projects is more than just marketing. It's also a great tool to get yourself

00:13:46.299 --> 00:13:51.299
brainstorming. When describing the original 3D modeling blog post I wrote about this,

